CA CMS Collaboration
TI Search for heavy resonances that decay into a vector boson and a Higgs
   boson in hadronic final states at root s=13TeV

CA CMS Collaboration
TI Measurement of the t(t)over-bar production cross section using events
   with one lepton and at least one jet in pp collisions at root s=13 TeV

CA CMS Collaboration
TI Search for high-mass Z gamma resonances in proton-proton collisions at
   root s=8 and 13 TeV using jet substructure techniques

CA CMS Collaboration
TI Search for single production of vector-like quarks decaying into a b
   quark and a W boson in proton-proton collisions at root s=13 TeV
